title: Alba Community Health Index Input
description: an input for entering Scotland's Community Health Index (CHI)
---

{% from "components/alba-community-health-index-input/macro.njk" import albaCommunityHealthIndexInput %}
{% from "components/label/macro.njk" import label %}
{% from "components/field/macro.njk" import field %}

<h2>Default</h2>
{% call field() %}
  {{ label({ for: "alba-community-health-index-input-demo", text: "Community Health Index" }) }}
  {{ albaCommunityHealthIndexInput({ id: "alba-community-health-index-input-demo" }) }}
{% endcall %}

<h2>Format</h2>
<p>10 digits encoding date of birth (DDMMYY) + two random digits + a sex digit (odd male, even female) + a Modulus-11 check digit.</p>

<h2>Reference</h2>
<p>See <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_Health_Service_Central_Register">Community Health Index</a>.</p>
